descriptionNullable: This custom-labeled dataset consists of hand gestures representing numbers 1-5 in American Sign Language. Collected and labelled personally, the dataset is tailored for Hand Gesture Recognition using YOLOv3. Available in both .txt and .yml formats, it serves as a valuable resource for training models aimed at interpreting sign language gestures.
